sources.title: High Gear (1933) PRE-CODE HOLLYWOOD
sources.description:
Stars: James Murray, Joan Marsh, Jackie Searl
Director: Leigh Jason

After a race car driver skids into a fiery collision that kills his ace mechanic, he quits the dangerous sport to drive a cab for a living. But the promise of fame and fortune beckons him to return to racing, if he can only summon the courage.

sources.title: High Gear (1933) Action, Adventure Full Length Movie
sources.description:
When Mark 'High Gear' Sherrod (Murray) looses his nerve, the race car driver takes a job driving a taxi, but when he befriends a cute reporter and the young handicapped son of a deceased driver, he attempts to return to the track. 

Director: Leigh Jason 
Writer: Rex Taylor, Leigh Jason, Charlie Saxton
